@thetimmcgraw, @FaithHill, @nicolekidman, and @keithurban arrive at the 55th #GRAMMYs in 2013. 
Who do you want to see walk the red carpet this year? #GRAMMYVault

Tonight we honor music legends that brought lyrics and melodies to homes around the world during our #GRAMMYSalute To Music Legends on @PBS! 
@DwightYoakam performs a three song medley “Hobo Bill’s Last Ride,” “Mule Skinner Blues,” and “T For Texas” to honor Jimmie Rodgers. 
Russell Thompkins Jr performs "You Make Me Feel Brand New" and @Official_Dionne_Warwick performed “Then Came You” to honor Thom Bell. 
@AndraDayMusic performs “Mississippi Goddam" to honor Nina Simone. 
John Cale performs "Sunday Morning” and “I'm Waiting For My Man" to honor the Velvet Underground.

On Music’s Biggest Night there could only be ONE opening number! TUNE IN right now to "#GRAMMYs Greatest Stories: A 60th Anniversary Special" on @cbstv (9-11 p.m. ET/PT). Swipe ↔️ to see past opening performances 🎶
